.el .ds Aq '
.TH devin-mcp-help 1  "help " 
.SH NAME
devin\-mcp\-help \- Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin mcp help\fR [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
devin\-mcp\-help\-add(1)
Add a new MCP server
.TP
devin\-mcp\-help\-list(1)
List all configured MCP servers
.TP
devin\-mcp\-help\-get(1)
Get details for a specific MCP server
.TP
devin\-mcp\-help\-remove(1)
Remove an MCP server
.TP
devin\-mcp\-help\-login(1)
Authenticate with an MCP server via OAuth
.TP
devin\-mcp\-help\-logout(1)
Remove stored OAuth credentials for an MCP server
.TP
devin\-mcp\-help\-enable(1)
Enable a disabled MCP server
.TP
devin\-mcp\-help\-disable(1)
Disable an MCP server without removing it
.TP
devin\-mcp\-help\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
